---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Terms of Service - Spottly"
    description="Terms of Service for Spottly platform"
>
    <!-- Header with navigation -->
    <header class="bg-black border-b border-gray-800">
        <nav class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
                <a href="/" class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <img
                        src="/assets/images/logo.svg"
                        alt="Spottly"
                        class="h-6 w-auto"
                    />
                </a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <main class="bg-black min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
                <!-- Page header -->
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-16">
                    <div>
                        <h1
                            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4"
                        >
                            Terms of Service
                        </h1>
                        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-2">
                            Effective Date: 26.08.2025
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/terms-of-service"
                            class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm"
                        >
                            Українська версія
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Content sections -->
                <div class="space-y-12 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                    <div class="text-lg mb-8">
                        <strong>Welcome to Spottly</strong>
                    </div>

                    <p class="mb-8">
                        Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your use of the Spottly
                        mobile application (the "App"), provided by Leonid
                        Lystopadov, an individual developer of the Spottly App
                        ("we", "us", "our"). By using the App, you agree to
                        these Terms.
                    </p>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            1. Use of the App
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            By using the App, you confirm that you have the
                            legal capacity to enter into a binding agreement
                            under applicable law.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            2. Account Registration
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            To access features of the App, you must create an
                            account. During registration, we may collect your
                            email address. Optionally, you may also provide your
                            date of birth and phone number. You are responsible
                            for maintaining the confidentiality of your account
                            credentials.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            3. User Responsibilities
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-2">
                            <li>
                                Use the App for any unlawful, fraudulent, or
                                harmful purpose.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Attempt to interfere with or compromise the
                                App's security or functionality.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Infringe upon the rights of others, including
                                intellectual property rights.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            4. Intellectual Property
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            All content, design elements, and software within
                            the App are owned or licensed by us and protected
                            under intellectual property laws. You may not copy,
                            reproduce, or modify any part of the App without our
                            prior written consent.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            5. Availability & Modifications
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or
                            discontinue any part of the App at any time, with or
                            without notice. We are not liable for any disruption
                            or data loss caused by such modifications or
                            interruptions.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            6. Third-Party Services
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            We use third-party analytics tools, such as Firebase
                            Analytics, to understand and improve usage of the
                            App. These services do not access personally
                            identifiable data unless explicitly provided by you.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            7. Limitation of Liability
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            The App is provided "as is" and "as available"
                            without warranties of any kind. We disclaim all
                            warranties to the fullest extent permitted by law
                            and shall not be liable for any indirect or
                            consequential damages.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            8. Termination
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your
                            access to the App at our sole discretion if you
                            violate these Terms.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            9. Governing Law
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            These Terms are governed by the laws of Ukraine,
                            without regard to conflict of laws principles.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                            10. Contact
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            For any questions about these Terms, contact us at: <a
                                href="mailto:support@spottly.io"
                                class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300"
                                >support@spottly.io</a
                            >
                        </p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Custom prose styling for legal document */
    .prose h1 {
        color: white;
    }

    .prose h2 {
        color: white;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(55 65 81);
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .prose p {
        color: rgb(209 213 219);
    }

    .prose strong {
        color: white;
    }

    .prose ul,
    .prose ol {
        color: rgb(209 213 219);
    }

    .prose li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .prose a {
        color: rgb(96 165 250);
        transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .prose a:hover {
        color: rgb(147 197 253);
    }
</style>
